Germany’s Soffin to Raise Guarantee to EU400 Billion, FTD Says

-- B y   S h e e n a g h   M a t t h e w s
-- 
2011-12-09T06:23:21Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-12-09/germany-s-soffin-to-raise-guarantee-to-eu400-billion-ftd-says.html
Germany ’s Soffin bank-rescue fund
plans to accept corporate and government bonds and to raise its
guarantee to 400 billion euros ($533 billion), the  Financial
Times Deutschland  reported, citing draft legislation for
financial-market stability.  The rescue fund previously had a guarantee frame of 300
billion euros, the newspaper said.  To contact the reporter on this story:
